<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>오늘의 가계부</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/reset.css" />
    <!-- animate.style -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css"
    />

    <style>
      @import url(http://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/notosanskr.css);

      @media (max-width: 996px) {
        html {
          font-size: 14px;
        }
        img {
          display: none;
        }
        .title {
          font-size: 2rem !important;
        }

        .catchphrase {
          font-size: 1.3rem !important;
          margin: 0 auto !important;
          margin-left: 1.5rem !important;
        }

        .catchphrase p {
          padding-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        .container_right {
          width: 52vw !important;
        }

        .body_bg {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          flex-direction: column;
        }
      }

      @media screen and (max-width: 680px) {
        html {
          font-size: 12px;
        }
        .button {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          flex-direction: column;
        }

        .yes,
        .no {
          margin: 2em !important;
        }

        .yes {
          margin-bottom: 0.5rem !important;
        }

        .no {
          margin-top: 0.5rem !important;
        }

        button {
          width: 14rem !important;
          line-height: 1rem !important;
        }

        .title,
        .catchphrase {
          margin: 0 auto !important;
          margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important;
        }
      }

      @media screen and (max-width: 567px) {
        .button {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          flex-direction: column;
        }
      }

      @media screen and (max-width: 375px) {
        .button {
          margin-top: 2rem !important;
        }
      }

      /* --------------------------------------------------------------------- */
      .body_bg {
        background-color: #3784ff;
      }

      .box {
        font-family: "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;

        justify-content: space-evenly;
        margin: 100px 0px;
      }

      /* .pig {
        width: 40vw;
        height: 60vh;
        margin: 10px;

        position: flex;
        left: 5vw;
        bottom: 0.1vh;
        
        z-index: 5;
      } */

      .coin-container1 {
        background-image: url("/static/img/pig2.png");
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: 35vw 65vh;

        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-end;
        bottom: 0.1vh;
        z-index: 10;
      }

      .coin1 {
        width: 5rem;
        display: inline-block;
        animation: backInDown;
        animation-duration: 4s;
        animation-fill-mode: forwards;
        animation-iteration-count: infinite;
        transform: rotate(45deg);
      }
      .coin2 {
        width: 8rem;
        display: inline-block;
        animation: backInDown;
        animation-duration: 4.5s;
      }
      .coin3 {
        width: 9rem;
        display: inline-block;
        animation: backInDown;
        animation-duration: 3s;
      }
      .coin4 {
        width: 10rem;
        display: inline-block;
        animation: backInDown;
        animation-duration: 3.5s;
      }

      .container_right {
        width: 35vw;
        height: 50vh;
        margin: 30px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .team-name {
        margin: 1.3rem;
        font-weight: 700;

        color: #fff;
      }
      .title {
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 4.5vw;
        color: #fff;
      }

      .catchphrase {
        /* margin: 1.5rem; */
        margin-bottom: 0;
        height: 20vh;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
        color: #fff;
      }

      .button_box {
        height: 10vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      button {
        width: 8rem;
        line-height: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        border: none;
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        font-family: "paybooc-Light", sans-serif;
        box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1rem;
        transition: 0.25s;
        background-color: #fff;
        color: #3784ff;
      }

      .yes {
        margin: 20px;
      }
      .no {
        margin: 20px;
      }

      .yes:hover {
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        transform: scale(1.2);
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .no:hover {
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        transform: scale(1.2);
        cursor: pointer;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body class="body_bg">
    <!-- tutorial -->
    <div class="box">
      <div class="coin-container1">
        <img class="coin1" src="/static/img/coin.png" alt="coin" />
        <img class="coin2" src="/static/img/coin.png" alt="coin" />
        <img class="coin3" src="/static/img/coin.png" alt="coin" />
        <img class="coin4" src="/static/img/coin.png" alt="coin" />
      </div>

      <!-- <img class="pig" src="/static/img/pig2.png" alt="pig_tutorial" /> -->

      <div class="container_right">
        <p class="team-name">힘내조</p>
        <div class="title">
          <p>오늘의 가계부</p>
          <hr />
        </div>

        <div class="catchphrase">
          <p>1인 가구를 위한 간단한 기능부터 생활 꿀팁까지!</p>
          <p>오늘부터 가계부 작성하시고 알뜰한 삶을 얻어보세요👍</p>
          <p>저희 서비스를 이용한 경험이 있으신가요?</p>
        </div>

        <div class="button_box">
          <div class="button">
            <!-- 캘린더 페이지로 이동 -->
            <button
              type="button"
              class="yes"
              onclick="location.href='/main?category=카페'"
            >
              예
            </button>

            <!-- 소비성향 테스트로 이동 -->
            <button
              type="button"
              class="no"
              onclick="location.href='tutorial2'"
              ;
            >
              아니오
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
